OL,3,CITV drama about infected blood scandal
OL,4,C'could be harrowing story'
OL,6,FA man affected by the infected blood
OL,7,Fscandal has said a forthcoming ITV
OL,8,Fdrama will tell a "very compelling and
OL,9,Fharrowing story" if it portrays the
OL,10,Fcase "faithfully".
OL,12,FRichard Warwick, 59, received blood
OL,13,Fproducts to treat his haemophilia, a
OL,14,Fclotting condition, when he attended
OL,15,FTreloar's school for disabled children
OL,16,Fin Hampshire.
OL,18,FHe later discovered he was infected as
OL,19,Fa child with hepatitis B and had
OL,20,Fcontracted HIV.
