OL,3,CITV drama about infected blood scandal
OL,4,C'could be harrowing story'
OL,6,FITV announced on Thursday that it had
OL,7,Fgiven the go-ahead to a drama about
OL,8,Fthe infected blood scandal, after the
OL,9,Fsuccess of the channel's series about
OL,10,FPost Office workers fighting for
OL,11,Fjustice.
OL,13,FPeter Moffat ` who won two Baftas for
OL,14,FBBC series Criminal Justice and also
OL,15,Fcreated the screenplay for upcoming
OL,16,FNetflix film Scoop, about the Duke of
OL,17,FYork's disastrous Newsnight interview
OL,18,F` will write the series.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/14
