OL,3,CITV drama about infected blood scandal
OL,4,C'could be harrowing story'
OL,6,FMr Warwick, a member of the Tainted
OL,7,FBlood campaign group, told the PA news
OL,8,Fagency that he welcomed the commission
OL,9,Fbut wants the creators to remain
OL,10,Ffaithful to the facts and stories.
OL,12,F"It's very welcome as long as they
OL,13,Fstick to the facts and tell it how it
OL,14,Fis, because one of our main concerns
OL,15,Fis that it doesn't faithfully convey
OL,16,Fthe desperation and the suffering
OL,17,Fvictims have had to endure over many
OL,18,Fdecades," he said.
