OL,3,CITV drama about infected blood scandal
OL,4,C'could be harrowing story'
OL,6,F"And if they do, it will tell a very
OL,7,Fcompelling and harrowing story of what
OL,8,Fwe've had to endure for so long."
OL,10,FHe said he has the "greatest
OL,11,Fconfidence" in Moffat, having been
OL,12,Fassured that the production and
OL,13,Fwriters will be consulting those
OL,14,Faffected throughout the process to
OL,15,Fensure the facts on dates and
OL,16,Ftimelines are correctly portrayed.
