OL,6,FMr Warwick, from Scarborough, said he
OL,7,Fwatched the Post Office series
OL,8,Fmultiple times as he found it "so
OL,9,Fcompelling" and hopes the infected
OL,10,Fblood scandal dramatisation has the
OL,11,Fsame impact.
OL,13,FHe said: "There was a Post Office on
OL,14,Fjust about every high street so that's
OL,15,Fvery much in the psyche of the British
OL,16,Fpublic.
