OL,3,CITV drama about infected blood scandal
OL,4,C'could be harrowing story'
OL,6,F"Contaminated blood isn't a
OL,7,Fparticularly pleasant topic to be
OL,8,Ftalking about and I think you could
OL,9,Fpossibly turn a lot of people off,
OL,10,Fwhich is why it has to be so
OL,11,Fcompelling, that people are drawn in
OL,12,Fand they can connect with the
OL,13,Fcharacters.
OL,15,F"I think that's what will tip us over
OL,16,Fthe edge and make people sit up and
OL,17,Ftake notice and realise just how big
OL,18,Fof a scandal this has been."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOUzD@\O]
