OL,6,FMr Warwick discovered he had
OL,7,Fcontracted HIV in 1988, and a year
OL,8,Flater his wife became pregnant.
OL,10,FThey were advised not to continue with
OL,11,Fthe pregnancy due to the risk the
OL,12,Fchild could be infected.
OL,14,FCampaigners have previously pushed for
OL,15,Fthe infected blood scandal, in which
OL,16,Fthousands died in what is widely
OL,17,Frecognised as the worst treatment
OL,18,Fdisaster in the history of the NHS, to
OL,19,Freceive the same attention as the Post
OL,20,FOffice events.
