OL,3,CITV drama about infected blood scandal
OL,4,C'could be harrowing story'
OL,6,FMoffat said: "It's been a great
OL,7,Fprivilege to meet those infected and
OL,8,Faffected and to learn about what they
OL,9,Fhave been through.
OL,11,F"I'm ashamed to say that when I
OL,12,Fstarted researching this story I knew
OL,13,Fnext to nothing about it. I'm even
OL,14,Fmore ashamed that this ignorance is
OL,15,Fshared by nearly everyone I mention it
OL,16,Fto.
OL,18,F"The victims of this scandal have been
OL,19,Flet down again and again by the state
OL,20,F` I hope in some small way this drama
OL,21,Fcan help their voices be heard."
