OL,4,C'could be harrowing story'
OL,6,FThe drama "focuses on how
OL,7,Fhaemophiliacs and those with other
OL,8,Fblood disorders were contaminated with
OL,9,Ftainted blood infecting them with HIV
OL,10,Fand Hepatitis C" during the 1970s and
OL,11,F1980s, the broadcaster said.
OL,13,FThe series will also look at what
OL,14,Fdoctors, politicians and
OL,15,Fpharmaceutical companies knew about
OL,16,Fthe risk and the work done by victims
OL,17,Fand their families to bring justice.
OL,26,@nD@KOUrD@PO]
