OL,6,FITV's head of drama Polly Hill said:
OL,7,F"Peter's scripts are brilliant and do
OL,8,Fjustice to this important story, while
OL,9,Fbringing it to screen with real
OL,10,Fclarity and compassion."
OL,12,FDes Collins, senior partner of Collins
OL,13,FSolicitors, which represents 1,500
OL,14,Fvictims and their families, welcomed
OL,15,Fthe news.
OL,17,F"We have long been approached by
OL,18,Fdocumentary-makers but believe this
OL,19,Fparticular series will refocus public
OL,20,Fattention on the tragedy of the
OL,21,Finfected blood scandal," he added.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@XO]yD@AOU}D@XO]
