OL,6,F"We live in hope that, unlike the Post
OL,7,FOffice victims, it won't take a TV
OL,8,Fdrama to air before justice and
OL,9,Fcompensation is secured for our
OL,10,Fclients and the whole infected blood
OL,11,Fcommunity."
OL,13,FHe added that "all eyes" will be on
OL,14,Fthe Infected Blood Inquiry's final
OL,15,Freport in May.
OL,17,FThe inquiry has already made its final
OL,18,Frecommendations for compensation for
OL,19,Fvictims and their loved ones.
